Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:08.59,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Uematsu Ryuujirou (59)\NTeitan Elementary School Principal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:07.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Have you made up your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:09.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This is a rare opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:14.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If I'm chosen to serve as a juror, I plan to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:16.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:22.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about class in that case, just\Nfocus on your assigned duty instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:25.27,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, is that a new painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chairman from the PTA donated it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something off about the painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you've been selected to serve as a juror?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to our Detective Boys information network.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.47,0:00:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of case is on trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's this "duty of confidentiality".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not allowed to talk to you about the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What harm would it do if it's just a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just keep it between you and the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I said no, I mean no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Kobayashi sensei can do her job as a juror?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can worry about it after she's actually chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being Group\NQet ctive Conan is brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bemg Group
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:24.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,COURTROOM CONFRONTATION IV\NJUROR KUBAYASHI SUMIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:24.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Detention Center
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your trial is approaching as we speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you have not changed your\Ndetermination to plead not guilty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:39.67,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Iwamatsu Toshio (35)\NDefendant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I swear I didn't do it, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why did you submit a confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did tell the police that it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they pressed me with the fact that blood was on my clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the victim's blood found\Non your clothes upon your arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they mentioned the hair and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hair and footprints left at the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They insisted that they had all the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that why you signed the confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I only went in there to steal stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, that son of a gun had already croaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Son of a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just refered to the victim Ishigaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as a "son of a gun".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had you made his acquaintance prior to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:49.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am here to represent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how disadvantageous it might seem,\Nplease tell me the whole truth without hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said many times, I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prosecutor Kujou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you've decided to take on Iwamatsu Toshio's defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just had an interview with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:24.85,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kujou Reiko (33)\NProsecutor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:23.69,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,To think I'll be battling with you over\Nwhat's black or white at the jury trial...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:25.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyo District Court
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the principal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And about my class per our discussion the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've changed your class to a free-study period.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But these kids said they wanted to cheer you on\Nas well as participate in practical social studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sure Sensei would be chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In what kind of trial are you participating?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Duty of confidentiality! '
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then I need to attend the information session for the jurors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the first juror ever from our Teitan\NElementary School, so please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which of those trials is Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} responsible for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you came to watch Mom's trial too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Mom's first trial where jurors are involved, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And my class is on break for finals, so I'm anxious to check on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her opponent is that Madonna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just hope she doesn't embarrass herself in front of the jurors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The undefeatable Queen, Attorney Kisaki, versus\Nthe Madonna of prosecutors, Prosecutor Kujou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} will be'judging them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet this is going to be a trial you can't afford to miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll find an excuse to give the principal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:43.52,Signs,,0,0,0,,Real Estate Company President Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First Public Trial
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Court is now in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will the defendant please step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, will the prosecutor please read the charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant, Iwamatsu Toshio, with the\Nintent to engage in theft activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Broke into the residence of Ishigaki Tadashi,\Na real estate company president...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Located at Akebono City, Fourth District,\NBlock 5 through the study windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While searching for valuables in the room, he was discovered by\NIshigaki-shi who had returned home, and a confrontation followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then pierced the victim's abdomen with a knife in his possesion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mentioned "a knife in his possesion"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But has the murder weapon been identified yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it has not been found as of yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please strike the last statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Duly noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon used in the crime went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant was found loitering in the vicinity\Nof the crime scene, wearing bloodstained clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After interrogation, he admitted to his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The charges and applicable penal statute is murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Per Article 199 of the Criminal Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does the defendant agree to the charges?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I have the attorney's opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:10:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I plead not guilty on behalf of my client\Nwith regard to the charge of murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Court will now proceed to evidence examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, allow me to draw your attention to the autopsy report.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will the jurors please confirm it through your monitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are they watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe some images of the victim's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may be difficult for laypeople to endure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the task of jurors is to perceive the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is exsanguination\Ndue to trauma on the abdomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon is likely to be a sharp instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The length of th eblade is estimated to be 15 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Court will now proceed to witness testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:00.60,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hara Yukie (66)\NHousekeeper
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are the housekeeper hired by the victim, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been on the job for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell the Court what transpired at the time of crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I was cleaning the second floor that day like I always do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard something coming from downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the master said he wouldn't be back for his\Nmeal after playing golf, I thought I was imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just when I came downstairs after cleaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why's the window open?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No further questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any questions'from the defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time you arrived at the scene in question...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit was nowhere to be seen, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only saw the master collapsed and covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The jurors should note that the witness\Nis merely the primary discoverer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And recognize the fact that she did not see the confrontation\Nbetween the defendant and the victim claimed by the prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:36.20,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tsukano Tooru (46)\NVictims Brother-in-Law
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are the younger brother of the victim's late wife, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My occupation is director under President Ishigaki's supervision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand you witnessed the crime scene\Nwhile going to consult with the victim about work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I needed the president's prompt decision\Nregarding a business transaction, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:12:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsukano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Master is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, hurry and call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honorable jurors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president was my only family since my sister died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please deliver a severe punishment toward\Nthe culprit who robbed him of his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The jurors are now free to inguire for\Nclarifications or details pertaining to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, may I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you didn't locate the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean the culprit took it with him when he fled?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:14:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We considered the possibility and have conducted a\Nthorough search in the vicinity of his escape route...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But failed to discover anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My client was placed under an urgent arrest\Ntwenty minutes after the reporting of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would take fifteen minutes even after sprinting\Nfrom Ishigaki's residence to the place of arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is logical to conclude that my client lacked the opportunity\Nto dispose of the murder weapon outside the police search.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, where did the murder weapon go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That one just struck the Madonna's weak spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So far it's anyone's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you are looking at right now is the\Nstudy where the crime was committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit broke in through the\Nwindow and searched for valuables...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But was discovered by the victim as he arrived home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you have any questions feel free to raise them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, if you permit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Question!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Raising your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the painting in the room, is it possible that it's upside-down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same painting was in our principal's office, so I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We sure can't tell which side of the painting should be up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do with the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the process of our investigation, we\Nreceived no reports of the painting being moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My client also has no recollection of moving that painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does something like that really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a painting that's hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suppose that you are correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that pertain to our trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, let's forget about the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please continue the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The painting is upside-down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite all the mounting evidence against the defendant,\Nthe Madonna still couldn't deliver the final blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:22.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's having a rough time because\Nher opponent is that Attorney Kisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom really did her best, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For today, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I doubt that Madonna would throw in the towel that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, is your teacher's question bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Sensei is right about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who turned the painting upside-down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Sensei simply just mistook things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was just nervous because\Nit's her first time serving as a juror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the painting really is upside-down, there must be a reason why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone's already ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we wait until Mom gets here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, who cares about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake he collapsed here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well fancy seeing the great detective here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does Attorney Kisaki require anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm only here to check out the crime scene of this trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I in your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just confirming some matters for our next trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you've obtained decisive evidence\Nthat can turn the situation in your favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you investigate the painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, one of the jurors mentioned it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, isn't it that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said it was upside-down, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, why don't you compare it\Nto the image you found on the website?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} said, this painting is indeed upside-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, what on earth does that have to do with the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way the owner of the painting would\Nmistake its orientation, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, exactly who hung it upside-down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remove the painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was stuck on the metal wall with a magnet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bloodstain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It makes sense if it's on the outside, but why\Nshould the blood get on the inner cover?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps someone touched it with their bloody hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An IOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has the borrower's acknowledgment, and a fingerprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used the painting as a secret safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An IOU with the amount of three million yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The borrower was Iwamatsu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the defendant's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the defendant's motive of theft was\Nactually regarding this IOU, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This will become quite the surprising new evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that the president...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Engaged in questionable monetary dealings\Noutside of his regular trade prior to his murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what you mentioned, the president believed in\Nconfidentiality and didn't tell anyone, which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've heard that he had\Nsomething like that, hidden behind the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Question him for further details outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to tell Mom about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was the defendant who upended the painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he take away the most important thing, the IOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:19:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps just as he was checking the inside\Nof the painting after he'd taken it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He heard the housekeeper coming down from the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he carelessly hung it back and fled in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he had time to put the painting back,\Nwhy couldn't he just escape with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, he was in a frenzied\Nstate when he stabbed the man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He couldn't get his brain to think straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,IS THAT CLEAR!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner should've kept the important\Ndocument inside the painting a secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how did the culprit know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, shouldn't there be a vase on top of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, I don't see a vase despite there being a vase mat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The area around the missing vase was bleached by the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss, do you know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That vase belonged to the Madam and\Nwas placed there after her death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like the Master got rid of it recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a second I thought it was knocked off and\Nshattered as a result of the struggle with the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't find any vase fragments\Nduring the initial inspection of the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a keen sense of observation, I should note.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All he observed were useless things!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She looked pretty nervous when asked about the vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's hiding something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you discovered Iwamatsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s IOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've found the defendant's motive for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he didn't randomly choose this place\Nto break in and commit theft, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall submit this crucial evidence during our next trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better if you take back the not\Nguilty plea and enter a plea bargain instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to worry about my choice of defense strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say I didn't warn you when you\Nembarrass yourself in front of the jurors!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, you sure you'll be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom is the type of person who fires up when the going gets tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.51,0:22:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get out of her pinch, she needs to\Nexpose the truth behind this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the key to it should be the upended painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as the whereabouts of the missing vase.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:06.13,Signs,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.02,0:24:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The unexpected discovery stirred the whole court.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is inside the vase!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:09.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,COURTROOM CONFRONTATION IV\NJUROR KOBAYASHI SUMIKO
